reviewText: Im pretty sure this is how my debit card got hacked!!!!! The dvds were crazy cheap and when I got them, they didn't play....what other incentive was there go sell them at that price??
I purchased this item months back and was a waste of money! i was extremely excited to watch when it does not work at all. Do not buy its a blank DVD!!!
Same as other commenter - does not work in any devices. Requested refund.
Bought this set, and not one of them works with any of my DVD players, something is wrong with the discs would warn u not to waste your money like I did
